buff.description:
Gain a charge of +10 healing each time you kill a foe, five charges if you kill an enemy player. (Max 25 stacks; ends on down.)
(Only one attribute-stacking sigil can be active at a time.)

Inflict bleeding for 6 seconds upon critically hitting a foe.
(Cooldown: 2 Seconds)

On Hit: Inflict Vulnerability (10 seconds)
(Cooldown: 2 seconds)
Your next three attacks after swapping to this weapon while in combat have a 100% critical chance. <c=@reminder>(Cooldown: 9 Seconds)</c>

Your next attack after you swap to this weapon while in combat inflicts poison for 5 seconds.
(Cooldown: 9 seconds)
Gain 25% of your endurance when you swap to this weapon while in combat. <c=@reminder>(Cooldown: 9 Seconds)</c>
Gain 4 stacks of might (5 seconds) when you swap to this weapon while in combat. <c=@reminder>(Cooldown: 9 seconds)</c>

name: Arrow Cart Blueprints
description: Use to construct an arrow cart build site. The arrow cart's primary function is to deal moderate area damage to infantry. Range 2,500. Requires 40 supply to complete.

name: Ballista Blueprints
description: Use to construct a ballista build site. The ballista's primary function is to deal heavy single target damage to siege equipment and infantry. Range 3,000. Requires 30 supply to complete.

name: Catapult Blueprints
description: Use to construct a catapult build site. The catapult's primary function is to deal heavy area damage to walls or moderate damage to gates. Range 4,000. Requires 40 supply to complete.

name: Alpha Siege Golem Blueprints
description: Use to construct an alpha siege golem build site. The siege golem's primary function is to deal heavy damage to gates. Range 225. It is the only mobile siege weapon. Requires 100 supply to complete.

name: Trebuchet Blueprints
description: Use to construct a trebuchet build site. The trebuchet's primary function is to deal heavy area damage to walls, or moderate damage to gates. Range 10,000. Requires 100 supply to complete.

name: Flame Ram Blueprints
description: Use to construct a flame ram build site. The flame ram's primary function is to deal heavy damage to gates. Unable to damage walls. Range 360. Requires 40 supply to complete.
